<p><b>What does it mean to be an outsider essay?</b> Being An Outsider Essay An outsider is a person who does not belong in a certain party or a group. An outsider is left out from parties, groups, and even sometimes they are not allowed near a place or person. Outsiders are not cool and people do not like them or are not drawn to them.</p>
